Title: Runaway Rusziona
Description:
Black whelps have the agility of a rock, but they try to make up for it with the most impressive top speed. Try to take it easy around those corners!

|TInterface\ICONS\Spell_Nature_Earthquake.blp:20|t|cFFFF0000|Hspell:398225|h[Eruption]|h|r: Dash forward.
|TInterface\ICONS\Shaman_PVP_RockShield.blp:20|t|cFFFF0000|Hspell:401260|h[Rock Halt]|h|r: Stops forward movement.
|TInterface\ICONS\SPELL_SHAMAN_EARTHQUAKE.blp:20|t|cFFFF0000|Hspell:401261|h[Earthen Will]|h|r: Restores all Vigor. Must be grounded.
ObjectivesText: Help Rusziona glide through the rings.

Objectives.Text: Start the Race at Celetiros and Complete It
